    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_4_3560-3631",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3560-3631",
      "markText": "而四大女作家——简·奥斯丁，艾米莉·勃朗特，夏洛蒂·勃朗特，乔治·爱略特——没有一位生育过子女，其中有两位没有结过婚，这一事实具有重大的意义。",
      "totalCount": 1598,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3560&rangeEnd=3631",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3560&rangeEnd=3631"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_4_1308-1328",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1308-1328",
      "markText": "英国的历史是男性的历史，不是女性的历史。",
      "totalCount": 765,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1308&rangeEnd=1328",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1308&rangeEnd=1328"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_4_8761-8843",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "8761-8843",
      "markText": "但是，要达到这一步，毫无疑问，我们就得盼望那个也许是神话传说中的黄金时代，到了那个时代，女人将会获得许久以来一直被剥夺了的东西——闲暇、金钱，以及一间她自己的房间。",
      "totalCount": 700,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8761&rangeEnd=8843",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8761&rangeEnd=8843"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_4_6883-6948",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6883-6948",
      "markText": "女性在一日之中的生活，往往没有给她们留下任何实质性的东西。她们所烹饪的食物已经被吃掉了；她们所养育的子女已经跑到外面的世界中去了。",
      "totalCount": 690,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6883&rangeEnd=6948",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6883&rangeEnd=6948"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_5_1730-1756",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1730-1756",
      "markText": "女人如果打算写小说，她必须有钱，还要有一间自己的房间",
      "totalCount": 656,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1730&rangeEnd=1756",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1730&rangeEnd=1756"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_5_7240-7269",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7240-7269",
      "markText": "不必匆忙。毋须闪光。除了自己本人之外，不必成为任何其他人。",
      "totalCount": 629,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7240&rangeEnd=7269",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7240&rangeEnd=7269"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_4_1804-1821",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1804-1821",
      "markText": "非凡的女性之产生有赖于普通的女性。",
      "totalCount": 612,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1804&rangeEnd=1821",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1804&rangeEnd=1821"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_5_3676-3722",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3676-3722",
      "markText": "为了保护他们那块被碾草机不断地滚压了三百年的草坪，他们把我那条思想观点的小鱼儿吓得躲起来了。",
      "totalCount": 520,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3676&rangeEnd=3722",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3676&rangeEnd=3722"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_5_13864-13925",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "13864-13925",
      "markText": "如果一个人饭吃得不好，他就不能够很好地思考，很好地恋爱，很好地睡觉。脊椎里的那盏感觉和思维之灯，用牛肉和梅子干是点不亮的。",
      "totalCount": 462,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13864&rangeEnd=13925",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13864&rangeEnd=13925"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_4_4902-4988",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4902-4988",
      "markText": "那种为了个人的原因而发出的呼吁，或者使一个书中人物成为某种个人的不满或牢骚之传声筒的愿望，总是会产生一种灾难性的后果：似乎使读者注意力集中的焦点，在突然之间由单一变为双重。",
      "totalCount": 425,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4902&rangeEnd=4988",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4902&rangeEnd=4988"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_4_6306-6385",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6306-6385",
      "markText": "当一位妇女着手写一部小说之时，她就会发现，她始终希望去改变那已经确立的价值观念——赋予对男人说来似乎不屑一顾的事物以严肃性，把他所认为重要的东西看得微不足道。",
      "totalCount": 408,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6306&rangeEnd=6385",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6306&rangeEnd=6385"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_6_2345-2384",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2345-2384",
      "markText": "为什么女人——据此书目来判断——在男人心目中要比男人在女人心目中更加有趣得多？",
      "totalCount": 396,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2345&rangeEnd=2384",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2345&rangeEnd=2384"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_10_2690-2850",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "2690-2850",
      "markText": "柯勒律治曾说，伟大的心灵总是雌雄同体两性因素并存的，大概就是这个意思。只有当两性因素融为一体之时，心灵才会才气横溢，充分发挥其所有功能。",
      "totalCount": 378,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2690&rangeEnd=2850",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2690&rangeEnd=2850"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_10_13711-13777",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "13711-13777",
      "markText": "保持自我比任何其他事情都重要得多。如果我知道如何说得崇高而动听，我想要对你们说，千万不要梦想去影响别人。只要就事论事，思考事物本身。",
      "totalCount": 377,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=13711&rangeEnd=13777",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=13711&rangeEnd=13777"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_6_12083-12140",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "12083-12140",
      "markText": "姑母的遗产的确向我揭示出一片蓝天，取代了弥尔顿建议我永远崇拜的那个高大魁梧绅士形象，是一望无际蓝色天空的开阔视野。",
      "totalCount": 340,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=12083&rangeEnd=12140",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=12083&rangeEnd=12140"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_8_7034-7125",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "7034-7125",
      "markText": "是那些被遗忘的古代诗人铺平了道路，驯服了天生桀骜不驯的原始语言。因为，杰作不是单独、孤立地产生的；它们是人们多年共同思索的产物，是群体思维的产物，因此在个人声音的背后，是群体的经验。",
      "totalCount": 336,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7034&rangeEnd=7125",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7034&rangeEnd=7125"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_7_842-878",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "842-878",
      "markText": "小说像一个蜘蛛网，或许是非常轻微地黏附着，然而却四个角都始终依附于人生。",
      "totalCount": 324,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=842&rangeEnd=878",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=842&rangeEnd=878"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_4_3937-4013",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3937-4013",
      "markText": "虽然她生活在普通的客厅里，被人们包围着，一位妇女所受到的训练，就是运用她的心灵去观察并且分析她的人物。她所受的训练，使她成为一位小说家，而不是一位诗人。",
      "totalCount": 323,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3937&rangeEnd=4013",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3937&rangeEnd=4013"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058814_4_5322-5378",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5322-5378",
      "markText": "那种艺术想象，不是太男性化就是太女性化了；它丧失了完美的整体性，与此同时，它丧失了作为一件艺术品最为基本的要素。",
      "totalCount": 322,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058814&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5322&rangeEnd=5378",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/bd4321b0813ab7d79g014f32?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5322&rangeEnd=5378"
    },
